This paper deals with deep neural networks for image matching, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also addresses the practical constraints of computational cost and model size, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of large and diverse datasets, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a new layer for convolutional neural networks, which is a topic related to neural networks (cs.NE).
